  "time_ut": 1661307800,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Problem in running the train service",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Railway Trade Union Confederation said that there is a problem in running the train service due to lack of materials required for maintenance of the train engine and passenger areas.",
        "It has also been informed that the said 20 trains will be in service for a short period of time.",
        "Meanwhile, it has been reported that there is a shortage of stones, planks, rails and nails for the maintenance of railway crossings. (a)"
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
